	<entry>
		<title>pt-BR para Joomla 5.0.3</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://backup/ribamar/index.php/joomla/pt-br-para-joomla-5-0-3"/>
		<published>2024-03-29T20:02:39-03:00</published>
		<updated>2024-03-29T20:02:39-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://backup/ribamar/index.php/joomla/pt-br-para-joomla-5-0-3</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;float-none&quot; style=&quot;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&quot; src=&quot;http://backup/ribamar/images/ptbr.jpeg&quot; width=&quot;637&quot; height=&quot;358&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Tradução para o pt-BR no Joomla 5.0.3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Como ainda não saiu a versão oficial da tradução do pt-BR para o Joomla 5, segue uma alternativa de ter o Joomla 5.0.3 em pt-BR.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baixar o pacote para o Joomla 4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4&quot;&gt;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Especificamente daqui&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4/downloads/joomla4-portuguese-brazil/4-0-3-1&quot;&gt;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4/downloads/joomla4-portuguese-brazil/4-0-3-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Descompactar e copiar as pastas pt-BR do pacote para o Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;administrator - language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;api - language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para as mesmas pastas do Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Entçao acessar o administrator do Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;System - Discovery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selecionar tudo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Discovery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Após instalar tornar o pt-BR o idioma default para o site e paara o administrator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;System - Languages&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Em Site clicar na coluna Default para pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selecionar Administrator (na combo com Site) e tornar pt-BR o default&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Caso chegue a faltar alguma palavra (até o momento não percebi) podemos criar uma substituição para ela.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sistema - Substituições de idioma&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;float-none&quot; style=&quot;display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;&quot; src=&quot;http://backup/ribamar/images/ptbr.jpeg&quot; width=&quot;637&quot; height=&quot;358&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Tradução para o pt-BR no Joomla 5.0.3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Como ainda não saiu a versão oficial da tradução do pt-BR para o Joomla 5, segue uma alternativa de ter o Joomla 5.0.3 em pt-BR.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Baixar o pacote para o Joomla 4&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4&quot;&gt;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Especificamente daqui&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4/downloads/joomla4-portuguese-brazil/4-0-3-1&quot;&gt;https://downloads.joomla.org/language-packs/translations-joomla4/downloads/joomla4-portuguese-brazil/4-0-3-1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Descompactar e copiar as pastas pt-BR do pacote para o Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;administrator - language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;api - language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;language - pt-BR&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Para as mesmas pastas do Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Entçao acessar o administrator do Joomla&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;System - Discovery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Selecionar tudo&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Discovery&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Após instalar tornar o pt-BR o idioma default para o site e paara o administrator.&lt;/p&gt;
